1
00:00:00,870 --> 00:00:04,780
Oh Jang Mi is desperate to see her mother.

2
00:00:05,110 --> 00:00:06,440
Don't you want to see her?

3
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:09,780
Jang Mi said she was coming to see me.

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:12,280
She said she was coming to see me.

5
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:14,390
Alright, then.

6
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:15,990
Let's go see Jang Mi.

7
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:18,690
We've been dying to meet her ourselves.

8
00:00:20,060 --> 00:00:24,560
Let's go together, ma'am.
Jang Mi misses you terribly.

9
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:37,210
Get out of the way! Let go!

10
00:00:40,210 --> 00:00:41,350
My goodness.

11
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:44,950
No! Here, over here!

12
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:47,590
Wait! Oh no!

13
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:50,120
Oh my goodness!

14
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:56,730
Won't we be in big trouble for this,
Hong Ju?

15
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,200
This is all your fault, Mom!

16
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:18,280
(Violent Crimes Unit 2)

17
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:22,250
(Yeongseo Police Department)

18
00:01:34,130 --> 00:01:37,140
Excuse me, have you seen Detective Kim?

19
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,700
He rushed out to a scene.

20
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,520
Tae Pyung!

21
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,850
Mom's gone. She's missing.

22
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:57,290
What? What do you mean, Mom's gone?

23
00:01:57,590 --> 00:02:00,230
I saw her take her cold medicine
and go to sleep before I left,

24
00:02:00,790 --> 00:02:03,630
but I just went back in,
and this is all I found.

25
00:02:04,630 --> 00:02:06,100
Whose is this?

26
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,130
Who cares whose it is right now?

27
00:02:09,730 --> 00:02:12,570
I think someone broke into our house
and took Mom!

28
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:17,840
Excuse me.

29
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,710
Is Detective Kim going to be much longer?

30
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:20,980
Could you please try to reach him for me?

31
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,080
It seems the investigation is
taking longer than expected.

32
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,320
Please wait a little longer.

33
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:29,320
It's okay. I'm sure he'll be here soon.

34
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,790
Hey, Tae Pyung.

35
00:02:34,530 --> 00:02:36,230
(Restricted number)

36
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:37,930
This is Kang Baek Ho.

37
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:40,370
What? Mom's missing?

38
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,810
Get out of the police station right now.

39
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:51,010
Or else...

40
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,980
you'll never see Jung Suk Hee again.

41
00:02:54,450 --> 00:02:55,450
Who is this?

42
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:57,980
Chae Hwa Young? It's you, isn't it?

43
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,450
What's going on?

44
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:02,190
We have to get out of here right now.

45
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:03,990
Otherwise, your mother's in danger.

46
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,290
Tae Pyung, I have to go.

47
00:03:06,290 --> 00:03:07,460
They took my mom?

48
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:10,460
Chae Hwa Young, are you even human?

49
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:12,960
Where is my mom? Where?

50
00:03:13,670 --> 00:03:15,130
Hello?

51
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,940
What do we do? They hung up.

52
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:22,110
First, let's get out of here.
We need to save your mother first.

53
00:03:22,570 --> 00:03:24,580
I'm not letting her get away with this.

54
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:26,540
I'll drag her to the abyss with me
if I have to.

55
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,880
Jang Mi.

56
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:34,220
Hey, Jang Mi, wait up! Jang Mi!

57
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,920
Hey, what's wrong?

58
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:44,700
- Are you hurt?
- No, it's just...

59
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:49,100
She must've pulled a muscle
since she hasn't exercised in a while.

60
00:03:50,970 --> 00:03:52,800
Shouldn't you go see a doctor?

61
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:56,410
No. I'll be fine if I just get some rest.

62
00:03:59,780 --> 00:04:01,750
I wonder why Jun Ho is calling.

63
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,020
Goodness.

64
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,220
Is there...

65
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:16,530
something going on
between you and Hong Ju?

66
00:04:16,690 --> 00:04:20,100
What? What do you mean?

67
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:23,070
You've been so jumpy,
like you're being blackmailed...

68
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,070
or something.

69
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:27,870
What? Blackmailed? Don't be ridiculous.

70
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:30,480
Why on earth would anyone threaten me?

71
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,650
Jin Hong Ju.

72
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:40,550
- Have you ever met Oh Jang Mi?
- What?

73
00:04:40,690 --> 00:04:43,720
I'm just wondering what kind of girl
would make Baek Ho so protective...

74
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:45,390
that he won't even let us meet her.

75
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:47,360
He hasn't even brought her home once.

76
00:04:47,490 --> 00:04:48,560
I don't know.

77
00:04:49,730 --> 00:04:53,030
Maybe he's not bringing her home
because of some history with your family?

78
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,430
You think so?

79
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:57,500
Baek Ho doesn't seem to be going
to Oh Jang Mi's hospital lately.

80
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:59,100
He still hasn't come home yet,
and I don't know where he is.

81
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,170
I'm calling to ask if you know anything,
Team Leader Jin.

82
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:03,540
I'm not sure.

83
00:05:04,210 --> 00:05:07,210
Seo Rin isn't back yet.
You don't think they're together, do you?

84
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,550
What? Those two?

85
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,020
When did they get so close
all of a sudden?

86
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:14,820
You just didn't know, Jun Ho.
She and Baek Ho have always been close.

87
00:05:15,850 --> 00:05:18,860
Anyway, it's just a guess.
I've got to go, Jun Ho.

88
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,430
For goodness' sake.

89
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:27,030
What am I going to do about this?

90
00:05:27,470 --> 00:05:29,870
I think the Chairman
is starting to suspect me.

91
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,770
Your affair?

92
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:34,540
What affair? I was the victim here.

93
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:37,680
I swear,
my conscience is completely clear.

94
00:05:37,740 --> 00:05:39,810
Then tell that to those photos
of your affair.

95
00:05:39,910 --> 00:05:42,050
Anyway, what do you think...

96
00:05:42,050 --> 00:05:43,950
Chae Hwa Young wants
with that half-wit woman?

97
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:45,420
That's what I was wondering.

98
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:49,320
Anyway, we weren't involved in this.

99
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:50,560
Got it, Mom?

100
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:53,360
Of course. Absolutely.

101
00:05:56,330 --> 00:05:58,600
Mom... Oh no, what do I do?

102
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,900
They said my mom was just sick
with a cold.

103
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:02,400
To do this to my mom...

104
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,470
Those bastards.

105
00:06:04,470 --> 00:06:06,570
What did your mother do to deserve this?

106
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:08,470
- Look.
- Let me see.

107
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:11,510
What do you want?

108
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:13,680
If you lay a finger on Jang Mi's mother,

109
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,610
I swear I'll kill you myself. Got it?

110
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:17,250
Tell me what you want.

111
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,880
If you want Jung Suk Hee to live,

112
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:21,350
bring Oh Bok Gil's cell phone
and memory card.

113
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,920
Where do I go?

114
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,190
Put Oh Jang Mi on the phone.

115
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,000
Jang Mi. It's for you.

116
00:06:34,730 --> 00:06:35,930
Is my mom okay?

117
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:39,500
If you dare touch a hair on her head,
I swear you'll pay.

118
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:42,210
Shut up. What could you possibly do?

119
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:45,340
I'll chase you to the end of the earth
and rip you to shreds.

120
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:47,150
I will drag you down to the abyss with me.

121
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,450
Run your mouth all you want.

122
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:52,180
I guess you don't want to save your mom,
Jung Suk Hee, do you?

123
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:53,990
I told you not to touch a single hair
on her head!

124
00:06:54,490 --> 00:06:58,220
Do that, and you won't get what you want.
You'll just end up in cuffs.

125
00:06:58,460 --> 00:07:00,990
You're getting cocky.
Maybe I should just hang up.

126
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,000
Okay, fine.

127
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,330
I'll give you what you want.

128
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:09,600
In exchange, let my mom go.

129
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:11,170
My mom is innocent.

130
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:13,370
Please, just let my mom go.

131
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:15,840
Aren't you the dutiful daughter.

132
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:21,050
Mom? Mom, are you okay?

133
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:23,180
Mom, just hang on a little longer.

134
00:07:23,610 --> 00:07:24,950
Mom, I'm coming to save you.

135
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:33,360
I'll give you what you want,
so let my mother go.

136
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:37,030
Fine. Then I suppose I can be generous.

137
00:07:37,530 --> 00:07:39,030
I'll text you the address.

138
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,470
Bring Oh Bok Gil's phone and memory card.

139
00:07:41,730 --> 00:07:44,270
But you have to come alone.

140
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:47,100
Otherwise, I can't guarantee
your mother will live.

141
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:49,910
- I understand.
- And if by some chance,

142
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:53,010
you show up with Kang Baek Ho
or some worthless cops,

143
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:55,550
Jung Suk Hee will meet the same fate
as Oh Bok Gil.

144
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:56,810
Don't you forget it.

145
00:07:57,420 --> 00:08:00,320
Unless you want to go shopping
for a funeral urn for Jung Suk Hee,

146
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:02,620
make sure that sinks in. Understand?

147
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:03,620
I get it!

148
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:07,990
But don't you dare lay a finger on my mom.
You hear me?

149
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,040
She wants you to go alone?

150
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:23,710
Yes.

151
00:08:24,010 --> 00:08:25,140
Once I get my mom back,

152
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:28,650
I'm going to make sure Chae Hwa Young
is in handcuffs this time, no matter what.

153
00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:30,350
Are you sure you should go alone?

154
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,150
It could be a trap set by Chae Hwa Young.

155
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,820
It could be a plot to kill you.

156
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:38,820
Don't worry. I'm fully prepared for this.

157
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:43,230
Since Chae Hwa Young can't find Seo Rin,
she won't dare act rashly.

158
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,400
Just a second.

159
00:08:49,330 --> 00:08:51,540
Tae Pyung. Let me borrow your motorcycle.

160
00:08:52,170 --> 00:08:53,970
And I need you to do something for me.

161
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:57,640
What?
You want me to get it ready and bring it?

162
00:08:58,580 --> 00:08:59,580
All right.

163
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:02,950
Well? What did he say?
Did he say Mom's okay?

164
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,220
I don't know yet.

165
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,920
Jang Mi has to go rescue Mom right now,

166
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:08,590
but it looks like
she needs a few things first.

167
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:18,730
If by some chance, Oh Jang Mi...

168
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:21,570
brings Kang Baek Ho
or the police with her, what do we do?

169
00:09:22,130 --> 00:09:24,600
We'll send a car
and make sure Oh Jang Mi comes alone.

170
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,470
I've put a man on Kang Baek Ho,

171
00:09:28,310 --> 00:09:30,070
so we'll get a call
the second he makes a move.

172
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,840
No matter what,

173
00:09:32,310 --> 00:09:35,410
we must get Oh Bok Gil's phone
and memory card.

174
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:37,180
They're critical pieces of evidence.

175
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:42,720
They might've made copies,
so smash the laptop to pieces.

176
00:09:43,450 --> 00:09:45,520
Yes, of course.

177
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:02,810
I'm sure they have someone out front
watching me.

178
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:06,110
If I make a move,
you and your mother will be in danger.

179
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:09,410
You're right.
Then you should stay here, Baek Ho.

180
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:11,180
No, just do as I say.

181
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,150
You think they'll fall for it?

182
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,420
We must make them, no matter what.

183
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:18,760
Okay.

184
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:22,430
I'll pull myself together
and go rescue my mom.

185
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:51,360
- Hey.
- Baek Ho. Jang Mi.

186
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:53,160
Look, I brought what you asked for.

187
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:55,430
- What?
- And your clothes.

188
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:56,860
Right.

189
00:10:58,500 --> 00:11:00,330
After Mom disappeared,

190
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:02,630
I found this handkerchief on the floor.

191
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:04,370
Is this Chae Hwa Young's?

192
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:08,270
Why is it so hot?

193
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:17,850
This...

194
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,950
It belongs to Yeom San Wol.

195
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,450
Could she be the one who took Mom?

196
00:11:22,690 --> 00:11:24,760
What?
You mean that old woman, Yeom San Wol?

197
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:26,690
Why would she kidnap Mom?

198
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,860
Chae Hwa Young must've put her up to it.

199
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,130
That old woman is unbelievable.

200
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:34,070
So she's been Chae Hwa Young's grunt
all along.

201
00:11:34,470 --> 00:11:35,470
I'm not so sure.

202
00:11:36,130 --> 00:11:38,700
Or maybe Chae Hwa Young
has something on her.

203
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:41,670
Maybe that's why they teamed up.

204
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:43,040
I won't let her get away with this.

205
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:47,010
It was creepy when she kept hitting on me,
but now this?

206
00:11:48,410 --> 00:11:50,110
I just hope our mom is okay.

207
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,580
I'm so sorry, Jang Mi.

208
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,620
I should have been taking better care
of Mom.

209
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,560
It's not your fault.

210
00:12:05,530 --> 00:12:08,630
Okay, it's all charged up. Here you go.

211
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:14,670
I'm just worried they won't fall for it.

212
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:16,070
Don't worry about it just yet.

213
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,680
Hey, Tae Pyung.

214
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:20,180
- Let's get changed.
- Alright.

215
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,880
Right, Jang Mi.

216
00:12:24,450 --> 00:12:25,450
Here...

217
00:12:26,050 --> 00:12:27,180
Tae Sook told me to give you this.

218
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:29,390
When did she get all this?

219
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:32,560
I guess she bought it
when you had that accident at the bank.

220
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:35,190
She might talk tough,
but she has a huge heart.

221
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:37,460
You know how much she cares, right?

222
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,630
Of course.

223
00:12:41,230 --> 00:12:42,600
If they lay a finger on my mom,

224
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,940
I'll zap every last one of them with this.

225
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:53,540
A moment of silence for the poor souls
who get in Jang Mi's way today.

226
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,550
- Let's do this!
- Let's do this!

227
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:15,530
Hello?

228
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,600
Oh Jang Mi.

229
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:20,300
You have Oh Bok Gil's phone
and memory card, right?

230
00:13:21,570 --> 00:13:23,310
They're just as they were
when I was about to go to the police.

231
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,240
It's not like I had to go find them.

232
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:27,980
So where do I go?

233
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,510
Wait.

234
00:13:37,890 --> 00:13:39,360
I can go by myself.

235
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:40,930
Hey, I said I'm going!

236
00:13:41,330 --> 00:13:42,330
Let go of me!

237
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,260
(479BA 6978)

238
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:05,980
It's 479BA 6978.

239
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:07,280
It's a black van.

240
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:11,390
Baek Ho, they're coming after me.
What do I do?

241
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:20,460
Don't panic. Pretend you're me.

242
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:23,170
They'll try to destroy my laptop.

243
00:14:23,770 --> 00:14:24,900
Just let them.

244
00:14:24,970 --> 00:14:26,040
(Oh Tae Pyung)

245
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:27,240
(They'll try to destroy my laptop.
Just let them.)

246
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:52,230
Just as you ordered,
we destroyed Kang Baek Ho's laptop.

247
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:55,370
It's beyond recovery,
even if he backed it up.

248
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:58,400
We've got Kang Baek Ho here.

249
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:05,880
Mom, are you okay? Mom!

250
00:15:11,420 --> 00:15:12,420
Oh Jang Mi.

251
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,850
Now that you've seen your mom,

252
00:15:15,250 --> 00:15:16,850
it's time you gave me what I want.

253
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:20,990
Here!

254
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:22,760
Take it.

255
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,560
Just let my mom go! Now!

256
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,070
This had better not be a fake.

257
00:15:28,970 --> 00:15:31,440
If you made a copy
or tried to pull a fast one,

258
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,700
it won't stop with your mother.

259
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:34,710
What?

260
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:37,840
You have more than just your mother
living in that house.

261
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:39,480
Like your brother, for starters.

262
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:42,450
And by the way, your niece is adorable.

263
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:44,210
Her name was Yeon Bo Ra, right?

264
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,320
- Yes.
- Shut your mouth!

265
00:15:47,450 --> 00:15:48,590
Mom.

266
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,890
Mom, are you okay?

267
00:15:49,890 --> 00:15:51,190
Are you hurt anywhere?

268
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,520
Jang Mi.

269
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:56,630
Suk Hee is in pain.

270
00:15:57,860 --> 00:16:00,300
Suk Hee wants to go home.

271
00:16:02,530 --> 00:16:05,200
You're burning up. Goodness.

272
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:10,070
Okay, Mom. Let's go home.
I'm so sorry you had to go through this.

273
00:16:10,270 --> 00:16:12,040
I'm sorry. Let's get you home right away.

274
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:15,180
What a dramatic mother-daughter reunion.

275
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,780
It's a shame I'm the only one
who gets to see it.

276
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:21,420
Chae Hwa Young.

277
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:23,250
Let my mom and me go.

278
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:24,620
You promised.

279
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:29,160
No!

280
00:16:29,430 --> 00:16:30,790
Don't you hit Jang Mi.

281
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:32,600
It'll hurt her. Don't hit her.

282
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:34,500
Jung Suk Hee, shut your mouth!

283
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:38,840
Or I can shut that mouth of yours
for good.

284
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,310
Chae Hwa Young is bad.

285
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,040
A very bad person.

286
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:46,380
She stole our Tok Hee. She's bad.

287
00:16:46,510 --> 00:16:49,280
Mom, calm down. I'm okay.

288
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,520
Chae Hwa Young.

289
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:53,780
Isn't what you did to my mother
enough for you?

290
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:56,290
Did you have to kill my father, too,

291
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:58,520
and then frame Professor Kang Nam Bong
for it?

292
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,320
How can you even call yourself human?

293
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:03,790
You've got a big mouth, don't you?

294
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:08,130
If you'd just died quietly back then,
I wouldn't have to be dealing with this.

295
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,200
Chae Hwa Young.

296
00:17:09,470 --> 00:17:12,170
You'd better remember this moment
and this day forever.

297
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:16,440
Don't hit Jang Mi. It hurts.
Don't hit Jang Mi.

298
00:17:16,510 --> 00:17:18,810
- Stop the nonsense and shut up!
- Chae Hwa Young!

299
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,080
You're the devil in disguise!

300
00:17:21,210 --> 00:17:23,250
What did my mom ever do to deserve this?

301
00:17:23,810 --> 00:17:26,450
- Let us out of here right now!
- Be quiet.

302
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:28,720
My baby died because of Jung Suk Hee.

303
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,490
What do you mean,
my mom is the reason your child died?

304
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,790
I read in an article
that you were pregnant.

305
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:35,630
So what if you had a miscarriage?
How is that my mother's fault?

306
00:17:35,930 --> 00:17:37,090
If that mother of yours...

307
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:40,930
hadn't shown up pregnant in front of me,

308
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:43,230
I never would have fallen
down those stairs.

309
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:47,100
The reason I lost my baby
is all because of your mother.

310
00:17:48,570 --> 00:17:50,070
If that hadn't happened back then,

311
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,510
by now,

312
00:17:52,110 --> 00:17:54,480
my child and I would be living
a happy life.

313
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:56,410
Stop with that ridiculous nonsense.

314
00:17:57,010 --> 00:17:58,850
What, did my mom push you
down the stairs or something?

315
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:01,850
You're the one who fell and miscarried.
Stop blaming my mother for it.

316
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,920
Shut up!

317
00:18:03,450 --> 00:18:04,690
Listen here, Chae Hwa Young.

318
00:18:06,260 --> 00:18:08,890
Your own greed brought this on you,
not my mother!

319
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:10,960
And my mom...

320
00:18:12,900 --> 00:18:15,600
No! Give me back my baby! No!

321
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,600
You stole her newborn, Seo Rin, from her.

322
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:26,040
And she threw herself in harm's way
to save me.

323
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:29,210
- It's all your fault!
- That's right.

324
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:30,750
If she had just died then,

325
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:33,080
she wouldn't
be ridiculed for being the idiot she is.

326
00:18:33,250 --> 00:18:34,250
Right?

327
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:35,990
Chae Hwa Young.

328
00:18:36,850 --> 00:18:39,390
You're not even human. You're a monster.

329
00:18:40,290 --> 00:18:43,060
I will bring the truth to light.
I swear I will.

330
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:45,530
The truth? Don't make me laugh.

331
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,970
Do you really think you're getting
out of here alive?

332
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:49,970
Manager Lee.

333
00:18:50,470 --> 00:18:53,000
Finish what you started. Get rid of them.

334
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:56,970
No!

335
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:58,740
Mom, no!

336
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:01,780
Chae Hwa Young,
you're breaking your promise!

337
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:03,780
You promised you'd let us go
if I brought you what you wanted!

338
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:07,420
A promise? Are you that stupid,
or just naive?

339
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:10,320
Don't you know that
promises are made to be broken?

340
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:12,320
Finish them off.

341
00:19:16,530 --> 00:19:18,800
Stay back. If you take one more step,

342
00:19:18,860 --> 00:19:20,900
I'll zap you all! Stay back!

343
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:22,630
What are you going to do with that?

344
00:19:24,170 --> 00:19:26,440
That's not even a gun. Give me that.

345
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,610
No!

346
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,540
Mom!

347
00:19:33,410 --> 00:19:36,210
- No!
- Get your hands off my mother!

348
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:43,450
Mom! Oh, no. Are you okay?

349
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:45,990
Don't you touch my mother!

350
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,090
Oh, no!

351
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,670
How dare you try to lay a hand on my girl?

352
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:04,510
Baek Ho?

353
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,620
- Jang Mi, are you okay?
- I'm okay.

354
00:20:15,850 --> 00:20:17,120
Baek Ho, be careful!

355
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:34,240
Baek Ho, behind you!

356
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,670
(Emergency alert)

357
00:21:13,010 --> 00:21:14,680
- What is this?
- What do you think?

358
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,780
It's the police.

359
00:21:16,050 --> 00:21:17,510
Chae Hwa Young,
did you think I wouldn't know your plan?

360
00:21:17,810 --> 00:21:20,420
Did you think I'd be reckless enough
to come here alone without the police?

361
00:21:20,650 --> 00:21:21,990
I don't believe this.

362
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:24,550
Mom, I'll untie you.

363
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:26,390
Mom, you've been through so much.

364
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:30,830
Chae Hwa Young. You think I'll let you
get away with this?

365
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:34,000
I will chase you to the end of the earth
until you've paid for all your sins.

366
00:21:34,100 --> 00:21:36,770
Fine. I'd like to see you try.

367
00:21:47,340 --> 00:21:48,380
Jang Mi, are you okay?

368
00:21:49,410 --> 00:21:51,420
- I'm fine.
- Ma'am, are you alright?

369
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,420
It's Baek Ho. Baek Ho's here.

370
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:56,290
Baek Ho, are you hurt?

371
00:21:57,090 --> 00:22:00,090
Were you always that good at fighting?

372
00:22:00,290 --> 00:22:02,760
I was in the special forces, after all.

373
00:22:10,370 --> 00:22:11,370
Oh, right.

374
00:22:12,070 --> 00:22:13,170
(Emergency alert)

375
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,770
Looks like our plan worked.

376
00:22:14,770 --> 00:22:16,610
You turned on the app at the perfect time.

377
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:19,580
- See? They all ran away.
- Thank you, Baek Ho.

378
00:22:20,010 --> 00:22:21,380
If you hadn't shown up when you did,

379
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:23,280
my mom and I really could have died.

380
00:22:23,780 --> 00:22:26,920
So, did the fake phone trick work?

381
00:22:27,250 --> 00:22:28,590
She didn't suspect a thing.

382
00:22:28,890 --> 00:22:32,020
She clearly never imagined
I could've swapped them so quickly.

383
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:35,790
And the footage on the memory card...

384
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,360
I've got it right here, safe and sound.

385
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:42,870
That's a relief.
Thanks to your quick thinking,

386
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:44,330
we were able to protect the evidence.

387
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:47,970
Come on, let's get out of here.
Ma'am, get on my back.

388
00:22:53,010 --> 00:22:54,010
Let's go.

389
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,730
All the evidence is gone now.

390
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:18,540
It all went up in smoke,
so we can relax now, right?

391
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,250
You're going to catch a cold.

392
00:23:29,980 --> 00:23:30,980
We should get going.

393
00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:32,250
Manager Lee.

394
00:23:33,950 --> 00:23:34,990
My Jun Ho...

395
00:23:37,590 --> 00:23:40,660
What will he think when he finds out
that I'm the culprit?

396
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,690
That won't happen, so please don't worry.

397
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:48,770
You're right.

398
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:56,040
This is...

399
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:59,040
the video and evidence proving
Chae Hwa Young is the culprit.

400
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:01,210
My dad's cell phone...

401
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:03,750
was found in the safe
in Chae Hwa Young's office.

402
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:04,750
This memory card...

403
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,220
has dashcam footage...

404
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,250
from the executive parking lot
at Dream Hotel.

405
00:24:08,390 --> 00:24:09,420
This one?

406
00:24:09,490 --> 00:24:10,720
On that dashcam footage,

407
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,390
there's a clip of CEO Chae
pushing Mr. Oh Bok Gil...

408
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:14,390
and causing his head injury.
It's the definitive proof.

409
00:24:15,130 --> 00:24:18,660
Detective Kim,
you must arrest CEO Chae this time.

410
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:20,660
And that's not all.

411
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:23,430
Chae Hwa Young kidnapped my mother,

412
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:28,440
and they said if we'd found her any later,
she could've developed pneumonia.

413
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:32,110
Please, make sure Chae Hwa Young
finally pays for her crimes.

414
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:36,110
All right. We'll reopen the investigation.

415
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,580
(Violent Crimes Unit 2)

416
00:24:43,890 --> 00:24:45,890
(Yeongseo Police Department)

417
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:48,630
Nice work, Jang Mi.

418
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:51,130
It was so smart of you
to make a fake phone.

419
00:24:51,530 --> 00:24:52,660
I'm so relieved you did.

420
00:24:53,630 --> 00:24:55,930
Chae Hwa Young has some
surprising blind spots.

421
00:24:56,330 --> 00:24:58,030
To think she actually believed
I'd give her the real thing.

422
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:10,980
What's the occasion?
You even made your rolled omelet.

423
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:12,620
I made it for Jun Ho.

424
00:25:12,620 --> 00:25:14,050
- Jun Ho, have some.
- Okay.

425
00:25:20,290 --> 00:25:22,690
They're going to reopen your case, Dad.

426
00:25:24,090 --> 00:25:26,730
What? What are you talking about?

427
00:25:26,930 --> 00:25:28,930
Reopen the case?
What are you talking about?

428
00:25:29,230 --> 00:25:30,430
You'll all find out soon enough.

429
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:44,250
Director Ma?
I wonder what she wants at this hour.

430
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,220
Hello, Seo Rin.

431
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:49,550
Is everything all right?

432
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:51,390
My car isn't running at the moment,

433
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:53,890
and I was wondering
if you could come pick me up.

434
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:56,030
We could even have a little date
on the way to work.

435
00:25:56,490 --> 00:25:57,490
Is that General Manager Kang?

436
00:25:58,230 --> 00:25:59,560
A date? I like the sound of that.

437
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:02,430
- I'll pick you up at your house then.
- Okay.

438
00:26:04,430 --> 00:26:05,500
What do you think you're doing?

439
00:26:05,840 --> 00:26:07,900
Why are you calling General Manager Kang
all of a sudden?

440
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:10,340
You'll see what this is about
when General Manager Kang gets here.

441
00:26:10,610 --> 00:26:12,710
No need for me to spell it out for you,
is there?

442
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:14,810
Breakfast is ready.

443
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:19,450
Grandfather.

444
00:26:20,050 --> 00:26:23,950
- Did you sleep well?
- I did. And you, sweetheart?

445
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,830
That was a delicious meal.

446
00:26:34,460 --> 00:26:37,730
Oh Jang Mi, you audacious little brat.

447
00:26:38,370 --> 00:26:40,900
You'll still pretend to be Seo Rin,
is that it?

448
00:26:41,770 --> 00:26:43,770
I could have killed you that day.

449
00:26:44,210 --> 00:26:46,680
The only reason you're alive
is that I still haven't found Seo Rin.

450
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:51,750
Mom, have some more of this. You love it.

451
00:26:55,120 --> 00:26:59,590
Grandfather, how about a round of golf?
It's been a while.

452
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:00,660
What?

453
00:27:01,690 --> 00:27:05,300
But you hate golf, sweetheart.
Suddenly, you want to play?

454
00:27:05,430 --> 00:27:06,530
I'd love to!

455
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,840
- Sounds like someone's here.
- Who could it be at this hour?

456
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,570
You'll see when you open the door.

457
00:27:15,970 --> 00:27:17,740
That was a great meal.

458
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:35,330
General Manager Kang.
Did you eat breakfast?

459
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:38,700
- Sorry for calling you in so early.
- I've already eaten.

460
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:41,600
I came to work with Director Ma,

461
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:43,730
but more importantly...

462
00:27:48,340 --> 00:27:49,370
What do we do?

463
00:27:49,470 --> 00:27:50,640
(Yeongseo Police Department,
Detective Kim)

464
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:52,480
I guess they found out
about the kidnapping already.

465
00:27:57,110 --> 00:27:58,110
Chae Hwa Young.

466
00:27:58,850 --> 00:28:01,250
You're under arrest
for the murder of Oh Bok Gil.

467
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,320
But...

468
00:28:44,860 --> 00:28:46,300
(The First Man)

469
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:48,300
The prosecutor's office issued a warrant
for her arrest.

470
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:49,770
This can't be happening!

471
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:52,940
This is a nightmare!

472
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:55,040
At the time, Professor Kang
of an undisclosed university...

473
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:56,510
Professor Kang
of an undisclosed university...

474
00:28:57,140 --> 00:28:58,140
That's you.

475
00:28:58,140 --> 00:29:00,710
Does that mean
Baek Ho was right all along?

476
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:03,050
The Chairman deserves to know
what CEO Chae did.

477
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:05,320
Why are you kneeling in front of me?

478
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,920
This is my chance.

479
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:09,050
I have to tell him the secret behind
my twin sister.

480
00:29:13,190 --> 00:29:15,190
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
